description: East Broadway 2 bedroom, 2 bath condo with deeded parking in a  Brownstone building. Features include; a Master Suite with private full private bath and a his & hers closet setup , A chef's kitchen that opens up into the dining area and living room that leads out onto a spacious private deck with views of the Boston skyline and the South Boston Seaport. Other highlights; nine foot ceilings, deeded storage ,a well-run, professionally managed condo association and Deeded Parking for one car. In addition, there are four condo association owned rental units (apartments) that help defray common area expenses.The condo fee includes Heat and Hot water. The unit has been completely renovated over the last three months...Line up!
